      <title>大众汽车田纳西工厂成立工会，为汽车联盟带来里程碑式的胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/volkswagen-union-vote-uaw-and-shawn-fain-win-key-plant-in-south</link>
      <description><![CDATA[田纳西州一家工厂的大众汽车公司员工投票加入汽车工人联合会，这是长期敌对的美国南部工会组织的一次里程碑式的胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/volkswagen-union-vote-uaw-and-shawn-fain-win-key-plant-in-south</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 02:15:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
